{"tid":1009091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長大巨如藏獒 寵物豬勿亂養","createTime":"2019-02-05T02:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T10:05:22.000Z","uid":56881,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"25af671b7c013c77de68e8a33a27483f9c4b85dc","tid":1009091,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:59:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%B7%A8%E5%A6%82%E8%97%8F%E7%8D%92-%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9%E8%B1%AC%E5%8B%BF%E4%BA%82%E9%A4%8A-014027022.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B7%25A8%25E5%25A6%2582%25E8%2597%258F%25E7%258D%2592-%25E5%25AF%25B5%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E5%258B%25BF%25E4%25BA%2582%25E9%25A4%258A-014027022.html&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=9ca8f057\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%B7%A8%E5%A6%82%E8%97%8F%E7%8D%92-%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9%E8%B1%AC%E5%8B%BF%E4%BA%82%E9%A4%8A-014027022.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hLHAyGXB5gYUNImOU4BpDA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/d4b57a8527c444666b5a943f9853134f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhLHAyGXB5gYUNImOU4BpDA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fd4b57a8527c444666b5a943f9853134f&h=7f26dad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【本報訊】幼豬外表可愛迷你，但長大後尺寸最大有如藏獒！漁農自然護理署獸醫師（動物衞生）曾然宙表示若非有關持牌人，一般人不能養豬，本港亦禁止寵物店出售小豬。他指本港屬於都市，環境並不適合飼養豬隻，提醒市民勿亂養小豬。<br />\n<br />\n曾續稱，本港無寵物豬獸醫服務，亦無相關配套，並說：「會有人訓練狗，豬就好少聽。」加上若從不合法渠道購買寵物豬，豬隻本身可能有病原，對人和豬都有害。他又說，「豬咁蠢」的說法並不正確，因豬的智商並不低，大約與狗隻相同，豬對人類更有多方面貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來香港唔養得豬仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a989bb914baaa76095442a344d615ba3dc9ef4","tid":1009091,"uid":64345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"成班港豬係晒度啦，點解唔養得？"},{"pid":"42a0fcc938ae6d3868d7e662d969b7b4aebb1b80","tid":1009091,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40a989bb914baaa76095442a344d615ba3dc9ef4","tid":1009091,"uid":64345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"成班港豬係晒度啦，點解唔養得？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T05:18:20.000Z","msg":"他指本港屬於都市，環境並不適合飼養豬隻，提醒市民勿亂養小豬。<br />\n<br />\n香港人縮影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb4745273411452da5ae8a44c89d9802f9e1ab2","tid":1009091,"uid":196552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42a0fcc938ae6d3868d7e662d969b7b4aebb1b80","tid":1009091,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40a989bb914baaa76095442a344d615ba3dc9ef4","tid":1009091,"uid":64345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"成班港豬係晒度啦，點解唔養得？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T05:18:20.000Z","msg":"他指本港屬於都市，環境並不適合飼養豬隻，提醒市民勿亂養小豬。<br />\n<br />\n香港人縮影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T05:22:03.000Z","msg":"但係飼養到咁多港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n豬都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d31fce9e176aa3ec88d0044d6c37e7c4f3f71a","tid":1009091,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T05:50:24.000Z","msg":"隻大豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2986ded2bf50f10a090c2100e75cc8ff74e0febe","tid":1009091,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"竟然有人養豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo